{"ts":"2026-06-26T20:17:34.686Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Detailing Agent Demos**\n\nI'm now detailing the first agent demo: Knowledge Search. It's a \"deep-reasoning\" agent for enterprise archives and telemetry. It will retrieve and synthesize data based on natural language queries, starting with an example thermal fatigue analysis. The agent uses GFF Embedder-v4 for semantic search, cross-references Oremesh data, and generates a failure mitigation report. My plans include a simulation log with timestamps and status updates.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
